        <title>INPUT SHAFT</title>
        <para>Install the main drive gear assembly approximately 1/2 inch into the main case, aligning either two marked
            timing teeth of the drive gear with the marked tooth of the left countershaft (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f13025f4">inset, Figure 154</hotlnk>).
        </para>
